Package: StableMCD
Type: Package
Title: Stability Approach for Parameter Selection in the Minimum Covariance Determinant and Least Trimmed Squares Problem
Version: 1.0
Date: 2024-08-17
Author: Qiang Heng
Maintainer: Qiang Heng <heng.qiang6@gmail.com>
Description: Using the notion the stability to produce instability paths that can be used to identify the proportion of outliers in the MCD and LTS problem. For the MCD problem,
it is also possible to select the number of principal components if spectral embedding is used.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.13), RcppArmadillo
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
